# Copy this file to .env and fill in your key(s).
# Run `node setup-keys.js` to do this interactively.
#
# Either key alone is fully sufficient for all 4 tools — both providers have
# a complete implementation of every tool. Setting both is only useful because
# the plugin routes each tool to its strongest backend.
#
# Routing when both keys are set:
#   nb2_generate / nb2_edit / nb2_upscale → Gemini (same NB2 model, one fewer hop)
#   nb2_smart_resize                       → fal.ai (purpose-built endpoint, Nano Banana Pro)
#
# Google AI Studio / Gemini key
#   Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#   Run:  node setup-keys.js --gemini
GEMINI_API_KEY=
#
# fal.ai key
#   Get a key at https://fal.ai/dashboard
#   Run:  node setup-keys.js --fal
FAL_KEY=
#
# At least one key is required.
